data.description: Come see the most lovely 3 bedroom, 2 bath custom  built ranch, with pleasing wrap around front porch! Upon entering, you will be greeted by the open concept living area, with beautiful hardwood floors  and vaulted ceiling. Living area flows nicely into the dining & kitchen space, which is graced with gorgeous granite countertops, sizeable pantry,  and nice bar area. Down the hall, the primary bedroom is quite spacious, with lots of natural light, en suite bath, as well as walk in closet! Two additional bedrooms, along with hall bath, and laundry area, make for perfect one level living! All stainless steel appliances, along with washer &  dryer will convey. This beautiful home sits on 2.54 acres, with apple trees,pear tree, and berry bushes. Large shed for extra storage, and lean to, as well as smaller shed with chicken coop to convey as well. Everything you need right here, with room to spread out, in desirable location! Call today  for your private showing!
